| Package        | Version   |
| -------------- | --------- |
| tailwindcss    | `3.4.3`   |
| postcss        | `8.4.38`  |
| autoprefixer   | `10.4.19` |
| daisyui        | latest    |
| postcss-loader | `8.1.0+`  |

